ClassDef.Name: NumberRange

Properties.Name: Min
Properties.Description: Determines the minimum value of the range.

Properties.Name: Max
Properties.Description: Determines the maximum value of the range.

Methods.Name: New
Methods.Description: Creates a new NumberRange object with the specified minimum and maximum values.

Methods.Name: Lerp
Methods.Description: Linearly interpolates between the minimum and maximum values of the range based on the parameter t, which is typically between 0 and 1.

ClassDef.Description: NumberRange is a data type that represents a range between two numbers, defined by a minimum and maximum value.
